window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Now aged seven and on the cusp of a class change, Peter desires to live a quiet life in his home village until he comes of age. </b></p><p> Unfortunately, Erryn, desiring access to his thoughts and memories, has other plans. When a routine trip to the forest almost turns deadly, Peter ends up where no child is supposed to be: hunting monsters in the town dungeon. </p><p><i>An Unbound Soul: Part 2: Dungeon</i> is the third volume set in Erryn’s world and the second in the continuing tale of Peter’s adventure.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p>"; 
